        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks for his book [<hi rend="italic">Physical geology and geography of Great Britain</hi>, 2d. ed. (1864)].</p> 
            <p>Pleased that ACR’s glacial lake theory is progressing. New Zealand lakes support the view. Suggests he write to Charles Gould in Tasmania, calling his attention to glacial action.</p>
        </abstract>
